Package com.g1.mychess.tournament.model

Class TournamentPlayer

java.lang.Object
com.g1.mychess.tournament.model.TournamentPlayer
@Entity public class TournamentPlayer extends Object
Represents a player participating in a tournament. Contains information about the player's registration, rating, progress, and status within the tournament. This class is mapped to the "tournament_player" table in the database.
